-- Halliburton says no longer working in Iran
-- 
-- Mon Apr 9, 2007 12:04pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/04/09/us-hallibuurton-iran-idUSWNAS586920070409

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Halliburton Co ( HAL.N ) on Monday said all of its commitments in Iran have been completed and it is no longer working in the country. 

 In January 2005, the company decided it would not accept new work in Iran but would complete its existing contracts there.